CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper February 15, 1958, pg. A19, reads: "Senior Assembly Vocalists - The Boys Octette of Fifth Ave. High School thrilled the Senior Assembly last Monday at ceremonies preceding the presentation of a vocational library to the school by B'nai B'rith. The eight-member singing group was directed by Richard Baugh. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Richard Baugh directing Fifth Avenue High School Boys Octette singing group on stage
